high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on your left.
Pick up the skillet on the counter.
Turn around and and open the fridge on your right.
Put the skillet into the fridge.
Remove the skillet from the fridge.
Turn around and put the skillet onto the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put the skillet into the fridge so that it cools.

high_descs: Turn around and move to stand in front of the copper pan on the island so the fridge is at your back.
Pick up the pan from the island.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Place the pan on the top shelf in the fridge, close the door, and then open the door to remove after a few seconds.
Turn around to face the center of the kitchen island.
Place the pan on the island just right of the center point.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table on your right.
Grab a baking pan from the table.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Put the pan in the fridge, then take it out.
Go to the kitchen table behind you.
Put the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan and replace it.
